args: I'll distract it! You guys scram!
Hah! Don't worry 'bout me, Chief.\nI'm used to a good tussle!
(Rgh! Definitely missin' that muscle right\nabout now. This won't be as easy as usual,\nbut...)
You ain't settin' one grimy claw on\nthese kids! Now, COME GET SOME!
(Hah. Look at that. My body's actin' on\npure reflex. Carefree playtime's all good\nand fun, but I've been missin' this!)
(Helpin' out the folks I want to protect,\nslammin' my enemies into the dirt...)
(This is me, baby! This is the only\nlife for Ranzal, the veteran merc!)
Ha HA, lookit that! Ran it smack into a\nboulder. Makin' use of the terrain is\nTactics 101.
Oooh, looks like he felt that one!\nNow, time to wrap this up.
Final score: Ranzal, 1. Fiend, 0.\n...You guys okay? Got all your teeth?
We're fine! Thank you so much!
That's years of experience at work, buddy.\nI eat chumps like that for breakfast.
But, uh... Speakin' of, I need to tell you\nguys something. It's kinda important.
Let's head back to the base. Won't have to\nworry 'bout any more interruptions there.
We can look up at the sky while we talk,\nsame as we did the day we first met...
Sooo, yeah... I've been dreading telling\nyou guys this, but here's the thing.
I'm movin' to a new town tomorrow.\nI know it's sudden, but...I won't be\nable to hang with you anymore.
Gosh. I'm really gonna miss you, Ranzal.
I'll miss you, too. I've said my share of\ngoodbyesâ€”hell, probably more than my\nshareâ€”but this might be the hardest yet.
(I mean that, too. Seriously.\nYou guys let me dream for a while.)
(But end of the day, I'm a grown man.\nTime to get back to reality and do my job.)
(It's a scary world out there. Somebody's\ngotta keep the peace so kids like you can\nhave the carefree childhoods you deserve.)
We didn't have long together, but it\nwas one hell of a ride. Thanks, you two.
I had a blast hanging out with you too,\nRanzal!
I'll never, ever, EVER forget you!
I won't either! Never ever!\n...Oh, yeah!
Here, take this. It's my prized possession:\na super shiny medal!
Ooh, you should take mine, too. Bet\nyou've never seen a bottle cap this cool!
Hey, now. If this stuff matters so much\nto you, shouldn't you hang on to it?
Take it! You're not just a normal friend,\nRanzal.
It was so, so, SO much fun playing with\nyou. Honest. Thanks for everything!
Awright, then. If you're sure, I'll take 'em.
A guy couldn't ask for a better set a'\nsouvenirs. I swear I'll treasure 'em always!
And don't think I'll be forgettin' you guys,\neither. Thanks for the great memories.
West woods're all clear of fiends, Cleo.\nWhere to now?
Already? Er, next would be...\nthe lake to the south.
You got it! Heh, watch out, pond scum.\nRanzal's comin' for ya!
What's gotten into you lately, Ranzal?\nYou always used to bellyache about having\nto hunt fiends, but now you're Mr. Eager.
Nothin' huge. Let's just say I...\nremembered my role in all this.
Thrashin' baddies, keepin' the peace...\nIt's all part of a day's work for the\ncommander of the Brat Brigade!
